This script tags and pushes a local Docker image to the Docker Hub.
# Script's arguments
Argument 1 (MUST)     : <DOCKER_SLUG> f.e. livingdocs/service-server
Argument 2 (MUST)     : <DOCKER_LOCAL_IMAGE>
Argument 3 (MUST)     : <GIT_BRANCH>
Argument 4 (MUST)     : <PULL_REQUEST_NUMBER> is a number or false
Argument 5 (MUST)     : <COMMIT_HASH>
Argument 6 (OPTION)   : <TEST_MODE>
# Script's environment variables
Env var (MUST)        : <DOCKER_USERNAME>
Env var (MUST)        : <DOCKER_PASSWORD>
